commit message: Remove the new line at EOF for 'md5sum' and 'version' files
Fix some pinyin format issues while parsing dictionary data.
Add a column in DB with pinyin without tones/spaces.
Add an average length for each words in translation to get better accurate results.
Add android min version code in version file for database update compatibility.
Add a 'starred_date' column in entries table.
Add column for french without accent.
Create index on PINYIN2 to speed up French/Pinyin queries.
Remove duplicates and trim every translation.
Change the way to generate the output file - The dictionary is now integrated in the app and not downloaded separately
